1
00:01:30,670 --> 00:01:37,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 11: THE COUNCILOR</font>

2
00:01:34,530 --> 00:01:38,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it's good I found her, 
but what are they up to?</font>

3
00:01:38,700 --> 00:01:42,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This reeks of a romantic 
rendezvous. Not a good look.</font>

4
00:01:42,730 --> 00:01:44,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know this won't fly, Miss Luna.</font>

5
00:01:45,350 --> 00:01:46,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, well.</font>

6
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:55,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Luna. I was wondering where 
you ran off to, but what's all this?</font>

7
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:59,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a good thing 
I'm the one who found you,</font>

8
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:03,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but this sorta thing is gonna 
get you another council meeting.</font>

9
00:02:04,460 --> 00:02:06,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously, would you cut it out?</font>

10
00:02:07,790 --> 00:02:10,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hate those meetings, for real.</font>

11
00:02:10,100 --> 00:02:12,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you even—</font>

12
00:02:10,770 --> 00:02:12,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Lize!</font>

13
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:16,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?</font>

14
00:02:16,580 --> 00:02:21,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After the riot back there, 
the air got really thick with poison.</font>

15
00:02:21,890 --> 00:02:22,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lize!</font>

16
00:02:25,610 --> 00:02:26,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh.</font>

17
00:02:27,340 --> 00:02:30,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the kid? The cursed youngling?</font>

18
00:02:33,380 --> 00:02:36,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck, kid? This ain't gonna do.</font>

19
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:40,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you still such 
a scrawny little runt?</font>

20
00:02:40,970 --> 00:02:45,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess it's just like Flame said. 
No point in letting you live, really.</font>

21
00:02:48,250 --> 00:02:51,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The cursed youngling. That label again.</i></font>

22
00:02:52,330 --> 00:02:55,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A name I don't know, but one 
that damns me all the same.</i></font>

23
00:02:56,450 --> 00:02:57,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lize!</font>

24
00:02:59,990 --> 00:03:01,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa!</font>

25
00:03:23,510 --> 00:03:24,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Luna.</font>

26
00:03:27,340 --> 00:03:28,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Witch—</font>

27
00:03:29,870 --> 00:03:32,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Found him! He's over here!</font>

28
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:35,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He used some kind of weird fan to 
rip the prophet's body to pieces!</font>

29
00:03:35,640 --> 00:03:37,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I saw the whole thing!</font>

30
00:03:38,230 --> 00:03:40,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait. Is that the poison mushroom witch?</font>

31
00:03:40,820 --> 00:03:42,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So they were working together.</font>

32
00:03:43,270 --> 00:03:45,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go get the authorities!</font>

33
00:03:45,490 --> 00:03:50,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like we're caught. 
I guess we should split.</font>

34
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:53,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll have to find a safer 
place to talk, Miss.</font>

35
00:03:55,290 --> 00:03:58,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know a safe place we could go.</font>

36
00:03:58,300 --> 00:03:59,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

37
00:04:03,990 --> 00:04:06,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Isn't that Henri?</i></font>

38
00:04:06,550 --> 00:04:11,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I didn't even need to summon him. 
My assistant was already here.</i></font>

39
00:04:12,500 --> 00:04:13,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Does that mean...</i></font>

40
00:04:13,810 --> 00:04:17,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>this outlaw rabble before me is 
what everyone is up in arms about?</i></font>

41
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:21,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Isn't that the crown prince?</i></font>

42
00:04:24,590 --> 00:04:26,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, let's get goin'.</font>

43
00:04:26,370 --> 00:04:28,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Henri! What are you doing?</font>

44
00:04:29,130 --> 00:04:31,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apprehend them!</font>

45
00:04:34,270 --> 00:04:36,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wind... magic?</i></font>

46
00:04:36,580 --> 00:04:37,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did they go?!</font>

47
00:04:37,620 --> 00:04:39,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They just disappeared!</font>

48
00:04:48,380 --> 00:04:51,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't smell like a liar,</font>

49
00:04:51,470 --> 00:04:55,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and we were in a rush, so I decided 
to take your advice, but...</font>

50
00:04:59,860 --> 00:05:05,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, where the heck are we?
 Is this your home?</font>

51
00:05:06,110 --> 00:05:08,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, this is—</font>

52
00:05:08,010 --> 00:05:09,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man!</font>

53
00:05:10,380 --> 00:05:12,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so pooped!</font>

54
00:05:13,650 --> 00:05:15,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First I had to blast
 The End of All Things,</font>

55
00:05:15,930 --> 00:05:18,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then teleport four people and two animals.</font>

56
00:05:18,810 --> 00:05:21,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been working so hard,</font>

57
00:05:21,570 --> 00:05:26,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but nobody ever thanks me!
 I mean, c'mon!</font>

58
00:05:26,130 --> 00:05:28,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Thank you.</font>

59
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:30,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Every word he says is garbage.</i></font>

60
00:05:31,140 --> 00:05:34,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you-know-who never 
even offers to help.</font>

61
00:05:34,650 --> 00:05:38,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, would it kill ya to grab me
 a glass of lemonade or two?</font>

62
00:05:38,870 --> 00:05:41,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}No, more than a glass or two.</font>

63
00:05:41,280 --> 00:05:44,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This room, with the way 
voices echo in here...</i></font>

64
00:05:41,510 --> 00:05:44,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'd need three, or four, 
or five, or six, or seven.</font>

65
00:05:44,150 --> 00:05:48,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Nah, I'd need more than lemonade. 
Maybe a really good meal instead.</font>

66
00:05:44,380 --> 00:05:46,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>seems familiar for some reason.</i></font>

67
00:05:48,490 --> 00:05:49,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lize?</font>

68
00:05:49,310 --> 00:05:53,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Ice cream, cake... something sweet. 
I wanna eat something nice and sweet!</font>

69
00:05:51,690 --> 00:05:53,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wonder why.</i></font>

70
00:05:54,490 --> 00:05:57,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really deserve a lot 
more praise than this!</font>

71
00:05:57,790 --> 00:06:01,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'm starving! Get me some food!</font>

72
00:06:01,170 --> 00:06:06,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Maybe I'll quit this gig. I just 
ain't cut out to be a black witch.</font>

73
00:06:05,150 --> 00:06:09,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want anyone to 
find out I know this guy.</font>

74
00:06:06,010 --> 00:06:07,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's such a scam!</font>

75
00:06:07,500 --> 00:06:09,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I wish I could work from bed!</font>

76
00:06:09,710 --> 00:06:15,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Wait, if I could work from bed, does 
that mean I would get to sleep all day?</font>

77
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:12,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should I shut him up?</font>

78
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lize, are you okay?</font>

79
00:06:19,190 --> 00:06:21,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They brought some lemonade.</font>

80
00:06:21,110 --> 00:06:24,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right. Gotta get down to business.</font>

81
00:06:27,100 --> 00:06:30,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like you guys were saying,
 I'm one of the council witches.</font>

82
00:06:30,660 --> 00:06:32,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Wind Magician.</font>

83
00:06:32,500 --> 00:06:34,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you... Lize, was it?</font>

84
00:06:37,060 --> 00:06:39,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the person sent to 
administer your surprise exam,</font>

85
00:06:42,730 --> 00:06:45,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and decide your fate 
as a cursed youngling.</font>

86
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:50,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Basically, whether you live 
or die is all up to me.</font>

87
00:06:51,640 --> 00:06:54,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sucks to meet like this, 
but let's get it over with.</font>

88
00:07:06,220 --> 00:07:09,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Recently, sometimes the 
things I write in my diary</i></font>

89
00:07:09,380 --> 00:07:12,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>don't match up with what I remember.</i></font>

90
00:07:13,450 --> 00:07:18,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The magical paper that Miss Witch 
gave me is made from mushrooms.</i></font>

91
00:07:18,850 --> 00:07:23,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When I write in it, the bad 
memories turn into yuck-shrooms.</i></font>

92
00:07:26,100 --> 00:07:32,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I felt kind of sad and uncomfortable 
watching the yuck-shrooms float away</i></font>

93
00:07:33,780 --> 00:07:37,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>so I decided to secretly 
keep another diary, too.</i></font>

94
00:07:38,520 --> 00:07:43,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sometimes, I find things written in that 
diary that I have no recollection of.</i></font>

95
00:07:44,730 --> 00:07:47,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even feelings and memories 
that would seem unforgettable</i></font>

96
00:07:48,370 --> 00:07:52,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>feel like they belong to some 
other person that I've never met.</i></font>

97
00:07:54,250 --> 00:08:00,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My legs get cold, like I'm on the verge
 of tumbling into a bottomless darkness.</i></font>

98
00:08:02,060 --> 00:08:03,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Other things also don't add up.</i></font>

99
00:08:04,580 --> 00:08:09,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wanted to hurry and catch up to Miss 
Witch, so I measured my height every day.</i></font>

100
00:08:09,830 --> 00:08:16,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, this is strange. I'm quite certain
 you were taller yesterday.</font>

101
00:08:16,020 --> 00:08:18,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why does it seem you've gotten smaller?</font>

102
00:08:22,630 --> 00:08:24,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Suddenly, I remembered one time</i></font>

103
00:08:24,460 --> 00:08:30,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>when Miss Witch had removed an animal's 
poison and turned it into a mushroom.</i></font>

104
00:08:37,820 --> 00:08:38,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

105
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:44,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems like this fellow is smaller 
now that you've absorbed his poison.</font>

106
00:08:45,170 --> 00:08:45,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh!</font>

107
00:08:46,680 --> 00:08:50,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay away from that! 
He sure doesn't learn, does he?</font>

108
00:08:51,100 --> 00:08:55,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It was strange when the rabbit went 
right back to the bug that stung him</i></font>

109
00:08:55,470 --> 00:08:57,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>as if nothing had happened.</i></font>

110
00:08:57,840 --> 00:09:02,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Miss Witch looked like she 
realized she'd committed a sin.</i></font>

111
00:09:06,760 --> 00:09:10,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Also, I can't explain how, 
whenever I was feeling bad,</i></font>

112
00:09:10,770 --> 00:09:14,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I would wake up the next 
morning completely refreshed.</i></font>

113
00:09:17,860 --> 00:09:21,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My questions became doubts, 
and as they collected deep inside,</i></font>

114
00:09:21,870 --> 00:09:24,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I felt like they were 
starting to suffocate me.</i></font>

115
00:09:26,660 --> 00:09:30,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why could I only grasp a vague 
outline of these doubts?</i></font>

116
00:09:30,810 --> 00:09:34,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why couldn't I trace them 
back to their source?</i></font>

117
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:41,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There was something I had to hold 
close to my heart and protect,</i></font>

118
00:09:41,890 --> 00:09:45,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>no matter how painful it became. 
Something that I must not lose.</i></font>

119
00:09:46,710 --> 00:09:48,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There was nothing more terrible,</i></font>

120
00:09:49,990 --> 00:09:52,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>more frightening than the 
thought of losing it.</i></font>

121
00:09:52,860 --> 00:09:56,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I strained my eyes to try to see 
the source of this restlessness,</i></font>

122
00:09:57,620 --> 00:10:00,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>so I could confront it, and then...</i></font>

123
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:02,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And then?</i></font>

124
00:10:11,270 --> 00:10:12,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah.</font>

125
00:10:12,920 --> 00:10:15,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lize just came to!</font>

126
00:10:17,220 --> 00:10:19,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay, Lize?</font>

127
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, yeah.</font>

128
00:10:21,420 --> 00:10:27,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The wind guy was such a jerk, 
it made you sick. We were worried!</font>

129
00:10:27,130 --> 00:10:28,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your problem, bull?</font>

130
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:31,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was unconscious?</i></font>

131
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:32,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

132
00:10:32,940 --> 00:10:38,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You make Luna manage your poison 
because you can't do it yourself?</font>

133
00:10:38,030 --> 00:10:39,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a pathetic kid.</font>

134
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:46,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Was Miss Witch trying to 
extract my poison just now?</i></font>

135
00:10:48,390 --> 00:10:50,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just got done saying 
"nice to meet you"...</font>

136
00:10:50,870 --> 00:10:52,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, you didn't.</font>

137
00:10:52,470 --> 00:10:56,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but at this rate, it's already 
like "farewell." Forever.</font>

138
00:10:56,460 --> 00:11:00,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you had a pretty generous 
grace period before I showed up.</font>

139
00:11:00,410 --> 00:11:02,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What were you doing that whole time?</font>

140
00:11:03,660 --> 00:11:07,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lize, don't run. I've got 
to get the poison out.</font>

141
00:11:09,890 --> 00:11:12,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, would you quit 
looking at me like that?</font>

142
00:11:12,890 --> 00:11:15,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nobody's looking at you like that.</font>

143
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:19,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, I'm really not doing this 
job by choice to begin with.</font>

144
00:11:19,990 --> 00:11:23,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I happened to skip one little 
meeting and they stuck me with it.</font>

145
00:11:24,540 --> 00:11:25,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lize.</font>

146
00:11:25,890 --> 00:11:28,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can do it by myself.</font>

147
00:11:28,340 --> 00:11:30,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quit acting so stubborn.</font>

148
00:11:31,210 --> 00:11:34,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We know you can't, that's 
why Luna's trying to help!</font>

149
00:11:32,230 --> 00:11:36,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I mean, I already had plans I couldn't 
back out of, and they treat me like this?</font>

150
00:11:35,970 --> 00:11:37,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've got to do something.</i></font>

151
00:11:36,910 --> 00:11:39,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's true I kinda wasn't 
in the mood, though.</font>

152
00:11:37,810 --> 00:11:42,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't let Miss Witch take 
away any more of my memories.</i></font>

153
00:11:42,760 --> 00:11:47,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I never want to make her doubt 
herself like that again.</i></font>

154
00:11:51,770 --> 00:11:56,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is way rougher on me 
than you. Yeah, poor me.</font>

155
00:11:56,500 --> 00:12:00,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So grin and bear it and don't 
hold it against me, Lize.</font>

156
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:06,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just accept my judgment 
and die for me, okay?</font>

157
00:12:08,250 --> 00:12:11,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you quit your endless 
blabbing for once, damn it?!</font>

158
00:12:11,560 --> 00:12:13,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut the hell up!</font>

159
00:12:16,670 --> 00:12:21,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! I'm a great magician here, 
ya crow-brain!</font>

160
00:12:21,210 --> 00:12:23,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Show me some respect, moron!</font>

161
00:12:23,430 --> 00:12:25,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't, I'm gonna tell Flame on you!</font>

162
00:12:25,740 --> 00:12:29,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Caw! Caw! Caw!</font>

163
00:12:26,390 --> 00:12:27,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ouch! Ouch, ouch, ouch, ouch!</font>

164
00:12:27,780 --> 00:12:29,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop it, you jerk!</font>

165
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:34,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Caw! Caw! Caw!</font>

166
00:12:30,750 --> 00:12:32,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please do something, Miss Luna!</font>

167
00:12:39,820 --> 00:12:41,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That guy is really something.</font>

168
00:12:41,580 --> 00:12:45,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never seen Luna glare at someone 
with that much contempt before.</font>

169
00:12:45,820 --> 00:12:51,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, it's pretty rare to find someone 
with no redeeming qualities at all.</font>

170
00:12:51,610 --> 00:12:56,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't the council members supposed to 
be really important black magicians?</font>

171
00:12:56,640 --> 00:12:59,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So why do you act so polite to Luna?</font>

172
00:13:00,190 --> 00:13:03,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm always polite to people I respect.</font>

173
00:13:03,870 --> 00:13:09,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you are? Well, I'm glad that 
you respect Luna. Thank you!</font>

174
00:13:10,390 --> 00:13:14,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, as a magician, 
Miss Luna is still my senior.</font>

175
00:13:15,100 --> 00:13:17,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess you do have decent 
manners after all.</font>

176
00:13:17,940 --> 00:13:19,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I dunno.</font>

177
00:13:19,860 --> 00:13:22,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish the crow would take 
a page out of your book.</font>

178
00:13:22,650 --> 00:13:23,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

179
00:13:23,860 --> 00:13:28,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As a fancy council member, you'd think 
needing emotional support from a bull</font>

180
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:31,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">would make the others think 
twice about that jerk.</font>

181
00:13:38,890 --> 00:13:43,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wonder what sort of experiences 
Miss Witch and that man shared.</i></font>

182
00:13:47,460 --> 00:13:51,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They refuse to look at each other, 
as if they can't face their emotions.</i></font>

183
00:13:52,140 --> 00:13:53,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I get the feeling that,</i></font>

184
00:13:54,350 --> 00:13:57,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>unlike me, he has had some kind of 
unforgettable experience with her,</i></font>

185
00:13:57,570 --> 00:13:58,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and it's suffocating to me.</i></font>

186
00:13:59,260 --> 00:14:00,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lize?</font>

187
00:14:00,370 --> 00:14:03,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I can't remember my time 
with her, no matter how long,</i></font>

188
00:14:03,990 --> 00:14:05,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>it might as well have never happened.</i></font>

189
00:14:06,380 --> 00:14:10,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Lize, what's wrong? Does it hurt?</font>

190
00:14:06,380 --> 00:14:08,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Like my memories and my growth,</i></font>

191
00:14:08,380 --> 00:14:12,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>this bittersweet suffering will 
continually be stolen from me,</i></font>

192
00:14:11,690 --> 00:14:16,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Lize? Don't struggle. 
It will be okay. Lize?</font>

193
00:14:12,780 --> 00:14:16,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>as long as I remain a cursed youngling 
who cannot stand on his own two feet.</i></font>

194
00:14:17,020 --> 00:14:19,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Since we can't truly share 
a connection with each other,</i></font>

195
00:14:20,050 --> 00:14:22,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>even when I'm with her, 
it feels like we're both alone.</i></font>

196
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:29,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>By spending time with her, it feels like 
I'm only intensifying her loneliness.</i></font>

197
00:14:29,700 --> 00:14:31,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And I hate that!</i></font>

198
00:14:35,900 --> 00:14:37,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lize?</font>

199
00:14:37,180 --> 00:14:38,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, what's that?</font>

200
00:14:44,350 --> 00:14:46,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing?</font>

201
00:14:46,910 --> 00:14:49,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that wolfsbane?</font>

202
00:15:00,280 --> 00:15:02,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lize, stop it.</font>

203
00:15:07,510 --> 00:15:12,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He discharged poison from his body 
to grow poisonous wolfsbane instead.</font>

204
00:15:12,720 --> 00:15:14,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a touching gesture,</font>

205
00:15:14,830 --> 00:15:17,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but if expelling a drop of poison
 tires him this much,</font>

206
00:15:17,310 --> 00:15:18,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there's not much point.</font>

207
00:15:20,700 --> 00:15:22,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't take it from me.</font>

208
00:15:24,980 --> 00:15:26,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It isn't fair.</i></font>

209
00:15:27,720 --> 00:15:33,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to be like him and grow into 
a person who is worthy of Miss Witch.</i></font>

210
00:15:34,220 --> 00:15:38,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But at this moment, there's nobody 
less worthy of her than me.</i></font>

211
00:15:40,290 --> 00:15:45,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Someday, I may even lose all 
of the feelings I hold for her.</i></font>

212
00:15:47,730 --> 00:15:51,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I lose sight of the kindness 
and sadness reflected in her eyes</i></font>

213
00:15:51,830 --> 00:15:57,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>as she was forced to pull the memories 
out of me with her own two hands,</i></font>

214
00:15:58,620 --> 00:16:01,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I may not be able to see her at all.</i></font>

215
00:16:03,980 --> 00:16:09,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even as I cling to her, these precious 
moments between us will melt away,</i></font>

216
00:16:10,190 --> 00:16:12,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>drop by drop, 
and there's nothing I can do.</i></font>

217
00:16:13,730 --> 00:16:18,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>By staying with her, this person 
I care for more than anyone...</i></font>

218
00:16:21,720 --> 00:16:25,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I may end up pushing her into 
a loneliness even darker than solitude.</i></font>

219
00:16:34,810 --> 00:16:36,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, but then again,</font>

220
00:16:36,890 --> 00:16:41,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">rattled as Luna is right now, maybe it's 
best she doesn't try to use her magic.</font>

221
00:16:45,620 --> 00:16:49,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I tried to ask, but 
where the heck are we?</font>

222
00:16:49,710 --> 00:16:52,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's been no reaction to us showing up.</font>

223
00:16:52,990 --> 00:16:55,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Must be a room somewhere in the castle.</font>

224
00:16:55,490 --> 00:16:58,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With a really strong barrier on it.</font>

225
00:16:58,490 --> 00:17:00,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, this is...</font>

226
00:17:00,740 --> 00:17:05,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hiding right under their noses might 
be safer than risking it out there.</font>

227
00:17:05,970 --> 00:17:08,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if this ain't your place, 
who's it belong to?</font>

228
00:17:10,540 --> 00:17:12,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are tons of birds everywhere.</font>

229
00:17:12,910 --> 00:17:15,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even the furniture and decorations 
are covered with birds!</font>

230
00:17:15,540 --> 00:17:17,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A real bird freak must live here.</font>

231
00:17:19,260 --> 00:17:20,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watch it!</font>

232
00:17:20,290 --> 00:17:24,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoever owns this place must 
be as dumb as he is obnoxious.</font>

233
00:17:25,020 --> 00:17:28,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I do get a feeling I've 
heard about it somewhere—</font>

234
00:17:28,140 --> 00:17:30,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for sharing your 
painfully incisive opinions.</font>

235
00:17:30,840 --> 00:17:35,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will take them into consideration 
when I next renovate, Wind Magician.</font>

236
00:17:36,810 --> 00:17:41,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It has been a while, yes? I'm glad you 
have found my home accommodating.</font>

237
00:17:44,140 --> 00:17:45,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}BIRD MAGICIAN</font>

238
00:17:48,760 --> 00:17:50,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master... Bird.</font>

239
00:17:54,210 --> 00:17:56,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Luna, I am glad to see you all well.</font>

240
00:17:58,500 --> 00:18:02,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Lize, nice meeting you. 
Or rather, nice <i>two</i> meet you again.</font>

241
00:18:03,810 --> 00:18:06,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am the Bird Magician.</font>

242
00:18:13,400 --> 00:18:16,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, don't get me wrong, Master Bird.</font>

243
00:18:16,130 --> 00:18:20,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A minute ago my mouth was, yeah, 
possessed by an evil spirit,</font>

244
00:18:20,180 --> 00:18:23,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and it made me say things I didn't mean.</font>

245
00:18:23,080 --> 00:18:24,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh?</font>

246
00:18:24,410 --> 00:18:29,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A black witch council member 
was possessed... by an evil spirit?</font>

247
00:18:30,740 --> 00:18:35,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I better get to a sauna to steam 
that spirit out so I'll catch you later.</font>

248
00:18:35,990 --> 00:18:37,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't move!</font>

249
00:18:37,980 --> 00:18:41,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You think I'm gonna let you get away 
that easy, you fraud of a magician?!</font>

250
00:18:41,090 --> 00:18:43,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Emotional abuse. Emotional Abuse.</i></font>

251
00:18:41,500 --> 00:18:43,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Caw!</font>

252
00:18:43,100 --> 00:18:44,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Emotional abuse. Emotional Abuse.</i></font>

253
00:18:43,670 --> 00:18:47,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are you calling a fraud?!
 Ouch! Ouch! Stop!</font>

254
00:18:44,510 --> 00:18:46,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Emotional abuse. Emotional Abuse.</i></font>

255
00:18:46,460 --> 00:18:48,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Emotional abuse. Emotional Abuse.</i></font>

256
00:18:48,100 --> 00:18:49,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Emotional Abuse.</i></font>

257
00:18:48,670 --> 00:18:52,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, now, Claw. Stop that. 
We are in Master Bird's presence.</font>

258
00:18:53,860 --> 00:18:56,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! That bird just spoke!</font>

259
00:18:57,140 --> 00:18:58,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look who's talking.</font>

260
00:18:58,860 --> 00:19:01,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My, you have such a foul mouth.</font>

261
00:19:01,690 --> 00:19:05,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am in the service of Master Bird
 as the butler of this manor.</font>

262
00:19:07,380 --> 00:19:08,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am Maximilian.</font>

263
00:19:10,280 --> 00:19:13,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please excuse this fledgling and 
accept my most sincere apologies,</font>

264
00:19:13,890 --> 00:19:15,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Excellency.</font>

265
00:19:21,060 --> 00:19:24,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He is not only a perpetual adolescent, 
but is also very obstinate.</font>

266
00:19:25,410 --> 00:19:27,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Claw, apologize to His Excellency.</font>

267
00:19:28,280 --> 00:19:29,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Claw?</font>

268
00:19:28,280 --> 00:19:29,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Emotional Abuse.</i></font>

269
00:19:29,890 --> 00:19:30,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it!</font>

270
00:19:31,550 --> 00:19:32,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Real sorry, man.</font>

271
00:19:31,970 --> 00:19:33,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Emotional Abuse.</i></font>

272
00:19:32,730 --> 00:19:34,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He isn't apologizing at all!</font>

273
00:19:35,580 --> 00:19:37,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Emotional Abuse.</i></font>

274
00:19:36,420 --> 00:19:37,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now Claw,</font>

275
00:19:37,900 --> 00:19:41,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't mind how despicable and pathetic 
your behavior or appearance is,</font>

276
00:19:39,230 --> 00:19:41,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Emotional Abuse.</i></font>

277
00:19:41,070 --> 00:19:45,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but you must not treat 
Master's guests with disrespect.</font>

278
00:19:42,820 --> 00:19:44,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Emotional Abuse.</i></font>

279
00:19:47,110 --> 00:19:48,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said it, bird.</font>

280
00:19:49,130 --> 00:19:51,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now get along, everyone.</font>

281
00:19:51,900 --> 00:19:53,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Bird Magician.</i></font>

282
00:19:54,420 --> 00:20:00,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If he's the master here, 
then this must be Claude's, um...</i></font>

283
00:20:00,210 --> 00:20:02,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Home? Nest?</i></font>

284
00:20:03,500 --> 00:20:09,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And yet, he looks just 
like a white magician...</i></font>

285
00:20:12,490 --> 00:20:15,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and we're inside the royal palace.</i></font>

286
00:20:15,970 --> 00:20:19,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Still, it seems like he's one of 
Miss Witch's black magician friends.</i></font>

287
00:20:20,140 --> 00:20:21,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What is going on?</i></font>

288
00:20:22,010 --> 00:20:27,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well then, let us no longer be distracted 
by Windy's incessant babbling.</font>

289
00:20:28,730 --> 00:20:29,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mm-hmm!</font>

290
00:20:30,710 --> 00:20:31,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Luna.</font>

291
00:20:32,290 --> 00:20:34,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh... Yes?</font>

292
00:20:36,670 --> 00:20:40,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Regarding the book store owner 
you had intended to visit,</font>

293
00:20:41,650 --> 00:20:46,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">as he is part elf, the miasma spreading 
in town had severely weakened him,</font>

294
00:20:46,540 --> 00:20:51,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I sent him one of my formulas, 
so he is no longer in immediate danger.</font>

295
00:20:52,550 --> 00:20:55,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Bird, you went out of your way...</font>

296
00:20:56,570 --> 00:20:58,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I sincerely apologize.</font>

297
00:20:58,410 --> 00:21:00,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank him, don't apologize!</font>

298
00:21:03,800 --> 00:21:06,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Judging from Wind's and Miss Witch's
 sudden change in demeanor</i></font>

299
00:21:06,850 --> 00:21:12,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and the crow's attitude, 
this must be a very important person.</i></font>

300
00:21:13,750 --> 00:21:17,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that a relief, Luna? 
But while cleaning the city,</font>

301
00:21:17,890 --> 00:21:20,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you meant to take the bookseller 
medicine too, right?</font>

302
00:21:20,850 --> 00:21:24,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not use a mushroom to teleport 
and drop in on him right now?</font>

303
00:21:26,250 --> 00:21:30,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps that would not be ideal 
for Luna in her unstable state.</font>

304
00:21:30,760 --> 00:21:35,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? But why? 
Why shouldn't she go see him?</font>

305
00:21:36,170 --> 00:21:40,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait. Miss Witch... is unstable?</i></font>

306
00:21:41,790 --> 00:21:44,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, Miss Luna is afflicted 
by a certain condition</font>

307
00:21:44,270 --> 00:21:48,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that's taboo for black witches, 
so her magic's weakened.</font>

308
00:21:48,830 --> 00:21:53,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's pretty obvious Miss Luna 
knows exactly what the cause is.</font>

309
00:21:54,540 --> 00:21:58,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should give me some credit for 
not spelling it out for everyone.</font>

310
00:22:00,580 --> 00:22:02,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Taboo for black witches?</i></font>

311
00:22:04,410 --> 00:22:05,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh!</i></font>

312
00:22:06,290 --> 00:22:09,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Love may be poison for black witches,</font>

313
00:22:09,130 --> 00:22:11,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it is a source of 
power for white witches.</font>

314
00:22:15,510 --> 00:22:19,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A condition taboo for black witches?
 Her magic is weakened?</i></font>

315
00:22:21,020 --> 00:22:23,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And she knows exactly what the cause is?</i></font>

316
00:22:29,620 --> 00:22:30,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's love.</i></font>

317
00:22:38,370 --> 00:22:41,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TRANSLATION: MICHAEL ARNOLD</font>

318
00:22:41,790 --> 00:22:46,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}SUBTITLE TIMING: ANDY ELLIS
EDITING: ELISABETH CRIST</font>

319
00:22:47,760 --> 00:22:52,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}QUALITY CHECK: GABRIELLA ALABANZA
TRANSLATION CHECK: MICHELLE TYMON</font>

320
00:24:06,650 --> 00:24:10,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}NEXT TIME: 
LIZE, THE BLACK WITCH'S APPRENTICE</font>

